Ansible Server OS: CentOS 7.x

--------- Ansible Install & Configuration Guide ---------

- To get Ansible for CentOS 7 add CentOS 7 EPEL repository is installed:
#sudo yum install epel-release
- Once the repository is installed, install Ansible with yum:
#sudo yum install ansible

- Disable Host Key Checking
Copy https://github.com/lorenzoeusepi77/kubernetes/ansible/config on "Ansible Server" /root/.ssh/ 

- Kubernetes Ansible hosts config 
Edit https://github.com/lorenzoeusepi77/kubernetes/ansible/hosts with Kubernetes Server hostname & ip address. 
Copy on on "Ansible Server" /etc/ansible/

---------- Installazione di GIT ----------
Install git with yum:
#sudo yum install git
Verify git version:
#git --version
